3 June 1977. Nigel and I catch Warsaw again, a few days after their Electric Circus debut. The Squat / sweltering day / Stuff the Jubilee banner / also new group The Fall who perform on the floor by an open door. Wrongly printed as 6th June. Pic via Manchester music archive. https://t.co/05Vu5I5YW1
